PURPOSE: Mark onboarding as complete and seed default data

WHEN TO CALL:
- After user completes all onboarding steps
- When user is on the congratulation screen

WHAT HAPPENS:
1. Marks onboarding_completed = true
2. Sets onboarding_completed_at timestamp
3. Seeds default data:
   - Account Groups
   - Voucher Types
   - Default Ledger Accounts
   - Default Banks (Nigerian banks)
   - Product Categories
   - Units (Pieces, Kg, Liters, etc.)
   - Shifts (for POS)
   - PFAs (Pension Fund Administrators)
4. Creates default roles and permissions:
   - Owner (full access)
   - Manager
   - Accountant
   - Sales Person
   - Cashier

NO PAYLOAD NEEDED - Just POST with auth token

